#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an10.194"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.194:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.194:0.2"
msgid "19. Ariyamaggavagga "
msgstr "19. The Noble Path "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.194:0.3"
msgid "194. Āsevitabbadhammasutta "
msgstr "194. Principles That Should Be Cultivated "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an10.194:1.1"
msgid "“Āsevitabbañca vo, bhikkhave, dhammaṃ desessāmi nāsevitabbañca. "
msgstr "“I will teach you the principle to cultivate and the principle not to cultivate. … "

msgctxt "an10.194:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an10.194:1.3"
msgid "katamo ca, bhikkhave, nāsevitabbo dhammo? "
msgstr "And what is the principle not to cultivate? "

msgctxt "an10.194:1.4"
msgid "Pāṇātipāto … pe … "
msgstr "Killing living creatures … "

msgctxt "an10.194:1.5"
msgid "micchādiṭṭhi—"
msgstr "wrong view. "

msgctxt "an10.194:1.6"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, nāsevitabbo dhammo. "
msgstr "This is called the principle not to cultivate. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an10.194:2.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, āsevitabbo dhammo? "
msgstr "And what is the principle to cultivate? "

msgctxt "an10.194:2.2"
msgid "Pāṇātipātā veramaṇī … pe … "
msgstr "Not killing living creatures … "

msgctxt "an10.194:2.3"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi—"
msgstr "right view. "

msgctxt "an10.194:2.4"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, āsevitabbo dhammo”ti. "
msgstr "This is called the principle to cultivate.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.194:2.5"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
